%% Smart Traffic Management System - Incident Report Sequence Diagram

sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User (Browser)
  participant API as Backend REST
  participant REP as Reports Service
  participant GM as Google Maps API
  participant DB as DB

  U->>API: Submit report(type, location, note)
  API->>REP: Validate + normalize payload
  REP->>GM: Reverse geocode (optional)
  GM-->>REP: Address metadata
  REP->>DB: Save IncidentReport(status=Open)
  REP-->>API: ReportId, status
  API-->>U: Confirmation + display on map
